### Create Task
POST http://localhost:8008/api/v1/tasks/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "email",
  "payload": {
    "to": "user@example.com",
    "subject": "Hello",
    "body": "This is a test task"
  }
}

###

### Create Task - Missing Type (should fail with 400)
POST http://localhost:8008/api/v1/tasks/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": {
    "key": "value"
  }
}

###

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:8008/api/v1/tasks/

###

### Get One Task (replace <task-id> with an actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8008/api/v1/tasks/task_a4805c05415224faa80e0117

###

### Delete Task (replace <task-id> with an actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8008/api/v1/tasks/task_a4805c05415224faa80e0117

###

### Delete Non-Existent Task (should fail with 404)
DELETE http://localhost:8008/api/v1/tasks/non-existent-id

###

### Get Non-Existent Task (should fail with 404)
GET http://localhost:8008/api/v1/tasks/non-existent-id
